hoox
====

hoox is a minimal inline-hooking library extracted and adapted from frida-gum.

It retains only the inline-hooking (Interceptor) capability and reimplements
its third-party dependencies in-tree, so that the shipped library has no
external runtime dependencies and can be amalgamated into a single hoox.c /
hoox.h (SQLite-style).


